  <p align="center"><strong><font size="+2">The Tree</font></strong></p>
  <p align="center">There was an image of a tree over the weekend. </p>
  <p align="center"> <img width="360" height="360" src="http://www.incedo.org.nz/Private/Email/Updates/20110330/TheTree.jpg"><br>
This tree has strong, aged, deep roots that help to sustain it, <br>
    allowing the tree to grow and flourish.</p>
  <p align="center">We were also reminded of an image that someone had a few years ago. </p>
  <p align="center"> <img width="296" height="447" src="http://www.incedo.org.nz/Private/Email/Updates/20110330/TreeFelled.jpg"><br>
Old trees need to be felled to allow light to penetrate <br>
